BBNaija Season 4 winner Mercy Eke has claimed she has never dated a married man. The BBNaija Pepper Dem winner made this revelation during a ‘Frankly Speaking’ show anchored by Pretty Mike and Nedu. Feeding a question on whether a side-chick solidifies marriage, the reality TV star disclosed that she has never been any man’s side-chick.   BBNaija: What will happen if Chichi and I align – Hermes     Tiwa Savage gushes over Tobi Amusan in surprise video call     #BBNaija: Sheggz justifies peeping at Chichi during bath   “I have never been a side-chick. I’ve never dated a married man,” Mercy boasted. According to her, if she chooses to become a side-chick to any married man, his wife should forget about him. “If I go that low to be a side-chick, aunty, I’m taking your husband. Sorry.”